title: Sekainohate De Aimashou
description:
All the chapters of Sekainohate De Aimashou. 

Summary From Mangahere:

Yona Ryouma, a normal high school boy, saves a man from another world at the cost of 

his own life when a mysterious earthquake occurs. The man, Emillio, uses a potion 

which apparently saves Ryouma's life. However, he is also changed into a girl in the 

process. Emillio is actually the prince of this alternate world and he declares 

Ryouma as his wife, presumably on the context of saving his life. But what about

Ryouma's life as a high school boy in his own world? And will he come to accept 

being the prince's wife?
